01:41.435 --> 01:49.508
<i> ¶ </i> ¶

01:51.212 --> 01:54.313
BUGLE: Each of our lives
is a story.

01:54.315 --> 01:58.283
<i> And every story is</i>
about a struggle.

01:58.285 --> 02:00.519
<i> A fight.</i>

02:00.521 --> 02:04.356
<i> A fight against sickness...</i>

02:04.358 --> 02:07.326
<i> poverty... [GUNFIRE]</i>

02:07.328 --> 02:08.527
<i> each other.</i>

02:08.529 --> 02:11.563
<i> [GUNFIRE]</i>

02:12.700 --> 02:15.601
<i> Some fight for big things.</i>

02:15.603 --> 02:17.503
<i> Ideas...</i>

02:18.305 --> 02:19.705
<i> freedoms...</i>

02:21.442 --> 02:23.308
<i> rights.</i>

02:23.310 --> 02:25.711
<i> ¶ ¶</i>

02:25.713 --> 02:27.913
<i> [COCKS GUN]</i>

02:27.915 --> 02:29.548
<i> [GUNSHOT] [GRUNT]</i>

02:31.352 --> 02:33.752
<i> Some fight for little things.</i>

02:33.754 --> 02:37.156
<i> A name, a piece of land...</i>

02:37.158 --> 02:39.191
<i> Or for a friend.</i>

02:40.794 --> 02:42.895
<i> The little liberties.</i>

02:44.632 --> 02:52.304
<i> [GUNFIRE CONTINUES]</i>

02:52.306 --> 02:55.941
<i> There's a fight</i>
inside men as well.

02:55.943 --> 02:57.843
<i> A fight against a reckoning.</i>

02:59.947 --> 03:02.781
<i> A reckoning of all</i>
the things we've done.

03:03.918 --> 03:05.784
<i> [GUNSHOT] [GRUNT]</i>

03:05.786 --> 03:08.587
<i> Or didn't do.</i>

03:08.589 --> 03:10.255
<i> [GUNSHOT] [GROAN]</i>

03:11.959 --> 03:15.894
<i> My granddaddy...</i>
He called it a warrant.

